To generate a new gpx route
visit http://www.bikehike.co.uk/mapview.php
Draw whatever you like
You can switch off Follow Road(Google Map) option, this option will automatically generate a route betwenn points that follows the road direction.
Click Save map, select "gpx route" and "download to file". Set a title and speed.
Click "Download route"
run processGPX code with
$ ./processGPX [GPX Filename]
one file at a time
